docs.description: Trade in Tools, Implements, Cutlery Of Base Metal - Nigeria. This data employs the subheadings of the original Harmonized System (HS1992). The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx

The National Accounts Main Aggregates database is produced and maintained by the Economic Statistics Branch of the United Nations Statistics Division (UNSD), with input from the UNSD, international organizations, and the national statistical agencies of more than 200 countries.  The database consists of a complete and consistent record of the main National Accounts of each UN member state, from 1970 onwards.  Records are based on official country data reported to the UNSD, supplemented with estimates for any years and countries with incomplete or inconsistent information. The National Accounts Main Aggregates database is produced and maintained by the Economic Statistics Branch of the United Nations Statistics Division (UNSD), with input from the UNSD, international organizations, and the national statistical agencies of more than 200 countries.
